How do I add a student? -click the 'add student' button on the home screen -Fill out the entry information appropriately (i.e number for age, word for age) -Click submit, the new students information has now been saved
How do I edit a students information? -click the 'edit student' button on the home screen -fill our the first and last name of the student you wish to edit -if found, information on the student will be pulled up -edit the information appropriately -save, your edited information on the student has now been saved
How do I view/print a report? -click the view report button -if you wish to open a report, click 'open report'. if you wish to customize a new one, click 'new report' -new selectable icons for your new report should appear, customize to your need -once finished, click submit
Problems? Make sure the program was installed correctly, reinstall if neccessary Make sure Excel 2003 or higher is installed Make sure you have at least 4gb of ram Make sure your operating system is windows 7 or higher Problem submitting infomation? Make sure correct formatting is used in text box entries
How to Uninstall Application (Read before doing) Click the clear files button two times for confirmation navigate to the location where you have stored the application files and delete them delete any additional reports created if desired Everything will then have been removed
